|=-----------------------------------------------------------------------=|
|=--------=[ Exploiting TCP and the Persist Timer Infiniteness ]=--------=|
|=-----------------------------------------------------------------------=|
|=---------------=[    By ithilgore                      ]=--------------=|
|=---------------=[       sock-raw.org                   ]=--------------=|
|=---------------=[                                      ]=--------------=|
|=---------------=[    ithilgore.ryu.L@gmail.com         ]=--------------=|
